2D Character Animator - Flash
- ,
Date Posted: 2014/05/01 13:08:01
Ref. JB3046329
Job Description
We are a Dubai based 2D animation Studio actively seeking several highly creative and talented 2D Character animation artists to join our expanding team..
The artist will be working closely with a team of animators and storyboard artists and contributing in brainstorming ideas to better the oberall project.
We work for clients such as Microsoft, Johnson & Johnson, RTA, Etisalat, du, PayPal, Western Union, Emirates NBD, ENOC and many more
The ideal candidate will have some background in storyboarding and concept art.
Job Description
nfamous Web Design LLC is currently looking to add an experienced digital Storyboard Artist to our busy production team. We're working on multiple high profile projects, so this is a great opportunity. Infamous offers health benefits and room to move up the ranks. If you are an awesome storyboarder and want to jump onto the busiest team in Dubai contact us.
Experienced digital Storyboard Artist for busy animation production studio.
• Must have proven storyboard skill. Preferably on broadcast series.
• Must have strong understanding of digital storyboard software.
• Must have the ability to produce solid boards. Take direction and complete revisions in a timely manner.
• Must have good creative vision and the ability to convey that vision through your storyboard.
• Must be flexible, willing to learn and be a motivated and motivating team player.
• Able to work within a production schedule.
• Must have good interpersonal skills.
• Must be a UAE resident, preferably Arabic speaking
This position is an excellent opportunity for highly organized and motivated digital Storyboard Artist who enjoys being part of an exciting, fast paced animation studio.
Skills
REQUIRED
Excellent skills in Adobe Flash 2D Character Animation
Free Hand
Concept art
Storyboard skills
Preferred
Experience in Explainer Videos
Arabic Speaking
Experience in Adobe Aftereffects
