About This Company
Passionate about what we doDue to websites such as YouTube and Vimeo, the Internet has undergone a video frenzy. Over 4 billion videos are watched on YouTube every day. By far, it has become the preferred media on the Web.We help our customers capitalize on the video phenomenon by producing engaging animated videos usually around two minutes or less in length that you use anywhere—on their Website, on YouTube or at trade shows—to help convert prospects into customers. We are a team of highly experienced animation storytellers who have created scores of videos for brands like du, PayPal, the Abu Dhabi Government, OSN and Emirates NBD—and we’re expanding our team.
